content:
yurydelendik opened PR #1993 from crates-obj to main:

Changes:

  • Moves object creation code from crates/jit/object.rs to the creates/obj (as ObjectBuilder)
  • Removes legacy crates/obj/function.rs
  • Removes write_debugsections

After this change, wasmtime wasm2obj will produce the same image as JIT compiler does. This makes it easier to inspect and troubleshot the generated code.

See also #1931
